Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to come to this dusty place with such strong ultra-violet rays?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have heard of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Runaway Express that runs on the desert without rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:00.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous train in the Sahara that hasn't stopped running for 100 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,100 years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it keep on moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems a Demon Tool is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:14.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If used for evil, it has the power to cause world-wide catastrophes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This Demon Tool is apparently being targeted by Arachnophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and securing the Demon Tool is our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Heated Runaway Express!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Tool Left by the Great Warlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:49.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your Shinigami skin, you don't get sunburn, right, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's no need to put on a mantle, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's because of my resistance to poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:01.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,that these three stripes reappear right away even after I dye my hair, which is quite annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A train station in the middle of the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for its arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spirits are oddly high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:19.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For over 100 years, it's been running on its assigned route, with perfect timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it were always precisely following its timetable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to see it once is a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to be a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a sightseeing spot after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, it sure is hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chibi! At least give us a proper greeting! Didn't your sister teach you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just click your tongue? Are you looking down on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you into minced meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:10.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... There are a lot of sand pits here, so play with your sis, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to the timetable, it should be about time it arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to the Runaway Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Good girl, good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:43.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That little kid is a bit suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}If this keeps up, it'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? If this keeps up, it'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:08.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The train always arriving precisely on time was a false rumor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What a let-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late, Shinigami's errand boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Fisher King, have already made the big catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Tool belongs to Arachne-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Arachnophobia's assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul protect release.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A witch response?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she wasn't a tourist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she might have been a tourist who was also a witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That witch had planted a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It left in the blink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a huge worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your thoughts for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and transform into guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:40.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're chasing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:41.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, {\alphaHFF}go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:41.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, {\alphaHFF}go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the first one on the train! I'll be taking the Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They've already caught up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Rod Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun, incoming attack from three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that? How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my Rod Bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I'll hide in the smoke and get close to the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun, the train is turning right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it sure is violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:14.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to watch out for attacks from both sides and above, then boarding the Runaway Express will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty, can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if I finish that enemy scum, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Rod-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,360° Kickflip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing skateboard tricks at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:59.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! This is the only place where you can find such massive sand banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do at least one or two tricks, it'll be an offense to the desert, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We're at the next bank already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty! No-Hander!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,3600°...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No-Hander!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Patty, return to weapon form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:52.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay on the roof, I'll just be a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It look likes the guy inside is further ahead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:17.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll detach this linkage and send those punks flying along with the rear carriages!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that pervert go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty fast, skateboard kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is goodbye. Disappear along with that carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He released the linkage, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! So there was another one in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you can't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! In a moment of confusion, I jumped to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's a total idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,An idiot! An idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:20.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz, Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Linkage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Linkage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the Demon Tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone near the engine room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz, Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Rod Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... His firepower is too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This train's power source...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Tool, {\alpha&HFF&}Eternal Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Tool, Eternal Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have the Demon Tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:50.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This Demon Tool belongs to Arachne-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our goal, the Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we can bring this runaway train to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wicked Demon Tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It really disgusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You ignorant Shibusen brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:48.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That Demon Tool is the work of the Great Warlock Eibon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon? That's probably just a useless villain anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon and Shinigami are the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're Shinigami's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the box where the Eternal Spring was stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying there's something inside this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spring alone is not the whole Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:27.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a set that includes both the key and the box it fits into.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... {\alpha&HFFF}Now... Now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Now... {\alpha&HFFF}Now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Now... Now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:36.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the plaque behind the box's cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon...{\alpha&HFF&} and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shi... {\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shi... Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:58.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake. This is my father's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my honorable father's signature on this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:12.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's written next to Eibon, the one you called the Wicked Warlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose signature is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:44.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me and the Africa branch's salvage unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, this guy's soul... {\alpha&HFF&}belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, this guy's soul... belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it down! Take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, a witch flew away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is the Eternal Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you kids, go take a rest at the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We have cold drinks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:50.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet again, another Demon Tool is in Shibusen's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find a single clue in the Level 1 information reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eibon and Shinigami are the same person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell is Eibon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:48.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to research in every book about a certain person, all the way up to the ones in the highest level block, Level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your student ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Star and Two-Star students only may go up to Level 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Teaching staff are allowed to go up to Level 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:06.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, both Death Scythes and first-class Technician all the way up to Level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You, sir, are still a One-Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not request anything but Level 1 books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the back of the card, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are the honorable son of Shinigami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:25.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll wait for a brief moment, I'll retrieve the requested book immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:26.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still a One-Star Technician.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If possible, I wanted to stand on equal footing with everyone, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:44.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like when I asked my father about the Kishin, he wouldn't give me a straight answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My only option is to investigate it myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:57.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in the Level 4 block, there is a single volume related to Eibon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please tell me which shelf it's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:00.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:07.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it hasn't been returned since it was last borrowed two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who borrowed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go myself and ask that person to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:26.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to my own incompetence, I can't determine who borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The signature on the loan card...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing but an "M" written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I deeply apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, who would borrow a book like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The book was borrowed roughly two months ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}April 1st...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day of the Kishin's resurrection...{\i0}
